OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FAlmost half of people want the UK
OL,8,FGovernment to back new oil and gas
OL,9,Fdevelopments ` more than twice the
OL,10,Fnumber who want the current ban on
OL,11,FNorth Sea drilling to continue, a poll
OL,12,Fsuggests.
OL,14,FA survey for Optimum found 49% back
OL,15,Fthe UK adopting a similar approach to
OL,16,FNorway and permitting new developments
OL,17,Fin the North Sea, while 24% want to
OL,18,Fsee Labour maintain its opposition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
