CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FOffshore Energies UK (OEUK), which
OL,8,Fcommissioned the polling, said it
OL,9,Fshowed that "the British public are
OL,10,Flooking for huge change in energy
OL,11,Fpolicy from the new Prime Minister".
OL,13,FWith more than 2,000 people across the
OL,14,FUK questioned earlier in July, the
OL,15,Ffindings were released ahead of Andy
OL,16,FBurnham taking over as Labour leader
OL,17,Fand prime minister amid speculation he
OL,18,Fcould spark a change in energy policy.
OL,26,@qD@MOUsD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FOEUK chief executive David Whitehouse
OL,8,Fsaid Labour supporters were "looking
OL,9,Ffor a significant shift in the
OL,10,FGovernment's flagship ban on new
OL,11,Fexploration".
OL,13,FThe research, carried out by Opinium,
OL,14,Fsuggested more than seven out of 10
OL,15,FBritons support the domestic
OL,16,Fproduction of oil and gas, compared to
OL,17,F8% who said it did not matter where
OL,18,Fsuch fuels come from.
OL,26,@pD@]OUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
