PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FOpening up new oil and gas fields was
OL,8,Falso the more popular option among
OL,9,Fthose who had voted Labour in the 2024
OL,10,Felection ` despite the party coming to
OL,11,Fpower on a commitment not to issue any
OL,12,Fnew licences.
OL,14,FWhile 35% of Labour supporters wanted
OL,15,Fto see this ban ` introduced amid
OL,16,Fconcerns over the environmental impact
OL,17,Fof fossil fuels ` remain in place, the
OL,18,Fpolling found 42% want the UK
OL,19,FGovernment to grant new licences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
