PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FMr Whitehouse said: "This compelling
OL,8,Fnew data shows that the British public
OL,9,Fare looking for huge change in energy
OL,10,Fpolicy from the new prime minister. "
OL,12,FHe added that voters have "had enough"
OL,13,Fof Britain's declining production of
OL,14,Foil and gas, which have "increased UK
OL,15,Fexposure to imports and geopolitical
OL,16,Frisk".
OL,26,@oD@UOUrD@eO]tD@[OUtD@fO]vD@YOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
