PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FThe OEUK chief executive stated: "All
OL,8,Fcorners of the UK population are
OL,9,Flooking for change from Andy Burnham,
OL,10,Fincluding the government's own core
OL,11,Fsupporters.
OL,13,F"Almost 70% of Labour voters said that
OL,14,Fthe UK should continue producing oil
OL,15,Fand gas in the North Sea rather than
OL,16,Frely on imports, compared to just 9%
OL,17,Fwho said it doesn't matter where it
OL,18,Fcomes from.
OL,26,@oD@bOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,F"Labour voters are also looking for a
OL,8,Fsignificant shift in the Government's
OL,9,Fflagship ban on new exploration. Only
OL,10,F35% of Labour supporters want the
OL,11,Fcurrent ban on new offshore licences
OL,12,Fto continue, with a clear majority
OL,13,F(42%) favouring Norway's much more
OL,14,Fpragmatic approach to allowing new
OL,15,Fdrilling offshore."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
