PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FAdding that Mr Burnham ` who is due to
OL,8,Fbecome prime minister on Monday ` is
OL,9,F"promising hope, to make sure that
OL,10,FBritain's industrial communities are
OL,11,Fnot left behind", Mr Whitehouse said
OL,12,Fthat "nowhere is this more desperately
OL,13,Fneeded than with the UK's energy
OL,14,Fsector".
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@PO]tD@FOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
