PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FHe insisted: "Domestic production is
OL,8,Fless carbon-intensive, supports the
OL,9,Fenergy transition, produces billions
OL,10,Fof pounds of tax revenues for the
OL,11,FChancellor, and builds industrial
OL,12,Fresilience across the country, making
OL,13,Fus all more secure.
OL,15,F"We need an energy policy reset to
OL,16,Fback North Sea oil and gas, not
OL,17,Fimports."
OL,26,@oD@NOUwD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
