OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784168292
OL,3,CVoters want 'huge change' in energy
OL,4,Cpolicy from Burnham as PM, polling
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FThe UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We have been a net importer of energy
OL,9,Ffor over 20 years, and new exploration
OL,10,Fin the North Sea would not change that.
OL,12,F"Oil and gas production will be with
OL,13,Fus for decades to come, and we will
OL,14,Fmanage existing fields for the
OL,15,Fentirety of their lifespan ` while
OL,16,Factively scaling up clean energy
OL,17,Findustries in the North Sea."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
